WEBVTT

00:00:01.163 --> 00:00:03.429
Once there was a star.

00:00:04.082 --> 00:00:06.804
Like everything else, she was born;

00:00:06.828 --> 00:00:10.609
grew to be around 30 times
the mass of our sun

00:00:10.633 --> 00:00:12.926
and lived for a very long time.

00:00:13.475 --> 00:00:14.843
Exactly how long,

00:00:14.867 --> 00:00:16.606
people cannot really tell.

00:00:17.162 --> 00:00:18.941
Just like everything in life,

00:00:18.965 --> 00:00:22.414
she reached the end
of her regular star days

00:00:22.438 --> 00:00:25.015
when her heart, the core of her life,

00:00:25.039 --> 00:00:26.505
exhausted its fuel.

00:00:26.905 --> 00:00:28.212
But that was no end.

00:00:28.236 --> 00:00:31.762
She transformed into a supernova,
and in the process